00:50:30.760 --> 00:50:35.830 align:middle line:84%
And in his hair is a
skull and a new moon,

00:50:35.830 --> 00:50:38.290 align:middle line:84%
the death and rebirth
at the same moment,

00:50:38.290 --> 00:50:41.410 align:middle line:90%
the moment of becoming.

00:50:41.410 --> 00:50:44.280 align:middle line:84%
>> That's a powerful image
for any life, not just--

00:50:44.280 --> 00:50:49.270 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, the goal of your quest
