00:50:52.640 --> 00:51:01.950 align:middle line:84%
which is fearless and
desireless, but just becoming.

00:51:01.950 --> 00:51:04.590 align:middle line:84%
This is the condition of a
warrior going into battle

00:51:04.590 --> 00:51:07.380 align:middle line:90%
with perfect courage.

00:51:07.380 --> 00:51:11.850 align:middle line:84%
