00:51:24.460 --> 00:51:25.980 align:middle line:90%
And that's the lifepoint in you.

00:51:25.980 --> 00:51:32.490 align:middle line:84%
And that's what these myths are
concerned to communicate to.

00:51:32.490 --> 00:51:35.580 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I've always
