00:51:46.840 --> 00:51:48.870 align:middle line:84%
And I don't know
what the word is,

00:51:48.870 --> 00:51:51.120 align:middle line:84%
and I don't even
know what flesh is.

00:51:51.120 --> 00:51:55.080 align:middle line:84%
But I know that there is
that experience of epiphany

00:51:55.080 --> 00:51:58.170 align:middle line:84%
when you meet what you don't
know and understand it.

00:51:58.170 --> 00:52:00.630 align:middle line:10%
>> Yeah, and you can
find it in yourself, too,

00:52:00.630 --> 00:52:01.920 align:middle line:10%
the word in yourself.

00:52:01.920 --> 00:52:04.170 align:middle line:84%
>> Where do you find it if
you don't find it yourself?

00:52:04.170 --> 00:52:11.100 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, Goethe says,
all things are metaphors.

00:52:11.100 --> 00:52:13.050 align:middle line:90%
[NON-ENGLISH].

00:52:13.050 --> 00:52:16.890 align:middle line:84%
Everything that's transitory is
but a metaphorical reference.

00:52:16.890 --> 00:52:18.660 align:middle line:90%
That's what we all are.

00:52:18.660 --> 00:52:20.580 align:middle line:90%
And to see the word--

00:52:20.580 --> 00:52:24.390 align:middle line:84%
we're getting back
to that your radiance

00:52:24.390 --> 00:52:28.750 align:middle line:84%
that we spoke of before
comes out here again now.

00:52:28.750 --> 00:52:32.860 align:middle line:84%
>> But how does one worship
a metaphor, love a metaphor,

00:52:32.860 --> 00:52:34.930 align:middle line:90%
die for a metaphor?

00:52:34.930 --> 00:52:38.580 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, that's what people
are doing all over the place.

00:52:38.580 --> 00:52:42.500 align:middle line:84%
That's what people are
doing all over the place,

00:52:42.500 --> 00:52:46.010 align:middle line:90%
dying for metaphors.

00:52:46.010 --> 00:52:48.860 align:middle line:84%
And when you really
realize the sound aum,

00:52:48.860 --> 00:52:50.960 align:middle line:84%
the sound of the
mystery of the word,

00:52:50.960 --> 00:52:53.040 align:middle line:84%
everywhere, then you
don't have to go out

00:52:53.040 --> 00:52:56.480 align:middle line:84%
die for anything because
it's right there all around.

00:52:56.480 --> 00:53:00.390 align:middle line:84%
And just sit still and see it
and experience it you know it.

00:53:00.390 --> 00:53:01.190 align:middle line:90%
>> Explain aum.

00:53:01.190 --> 00:53:03.200 align:middle line:84%
That's the first time
you've used that.

00:53:03.200 --> 00:53:08.060 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, aum is a word that--

00:53:08.060 --> 00:53:09.860 align:middle line:10%
what can I say--

00:53:09.860 --> 00:53:13.070 align:middle line:10%
represents to our
ears that sound

00:53:13.070 --> 00:53:15.980 align:middle line:10%
of the energy of the universe,
of which all things are

00:53:15.980 --> 00:53:18.980 align:middle line:10%
manifestations.

00:53:18.980 --> 00:53:23.720 align:middle line:90%
And aum is a wonderful word.

00:53:23.720 --> 00:53:30.440 align:middle line:84%
It's written A-U-M. you start
in the back of the mouth, ah.

00:53:30.440 --> 00:53:33.560 align:middle line:84%
And then, ooh, you
fill the mouth.

00:53:33.560 --> 00:53:36.180 align:middle line:90%
And mm closes at the mouth.

00:53:36.180 --> 00:53:38.270 align:middle line:84%
And when you have
pronounced this properly,

00:53:38.270 --> 00:53:45.020 align:middle line:84%
all vowel sounds are in
that pronunciation, aum.

00:53:45.020 --> 00:53:50.390 align:middle line:84%
And consonants are regarded
simply as interruptions of aum.

00:53:50.390 --> 00:53:54.140 align:middle line:84%
And all words are
thus fragments of aum,

00:53:54.140 --> 00:53:58.280 align:middle line:84%
as all images are fragments
of the form of forms

00:53:58.280 --> 00:54:02.390 align:middle line:84%
of which all things
are just reflections.

00:54:02.390 --> 00:54:06.410 align:middle line:84%
And so aum is a symbol,
a symbolic sound,

00:54:06.410 --> 00:54:10.100 align:middle line:84%
that puts you in touch
with that throbbing being

00:54:10.100 --> 00:54:13.340 align:middle line:90%
that is the universe.

00:54:13.340 --> 00:54:16.328 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING]

00:54:16.328 --> 00:54:25.685 align:middle line:90%


